383
00:32:42,920 --> 00:32:44,910
You are pretty, Patris.

384
00:32:46,060 --> 00:32:47,720
I...

385
00:32:48,930 --> 00:32:52,450
Well, Patris.
Master is waiting for you.

386
00:32:54,300 --> 00:32:56,490
Please make me your slave.

387
00:33:06,280 --> 00:33:07,640
I'll grant your wish.

388
00:33:14,020 --> 00:33:17,510
