389
00:33:23,830 --> 00:33:25,660
Diana, don't go!

390
00:33:28,400 --> 00:33:34,860
No, Patris. This is your first time.
You must be alone with your Master.

391
00:33:44,950 --> 00:33:51,440
She's good.
We'll get along just fine.

392
00:34:01,100 --> 00:34:03,430
Why am I so sad?

393
00:34:07,170 --> 00:34:09,870
