401
00:34:58,220 --> 00:35:00,020
You're an impossible slave.

402
00:35:00,090 --> 00:35:05,760
Forgive me, Master...
but, I can't help it.

403
00:35:10,470 --> 00:35:17,130
Please, Master. Take me!
I can't wait any longer!

404
00:35:17,610 --> 00:35:19,670
I wonder which of us is the Master.

405
00:35:19,780 --> 00:35:21,770
Please!

406
00:35:23,080 --> 00:35:25,070
Now, Master!

407
00:35:31,520 --> 00:35:33,990
Master, I'm so happy!

408
00:35:34,360 --> 00:35:37,260
Incredibly sensitive for a virgin.

409
00:35:38,230 --> 00:35:42,460
You told me once
I'd make a good slave.

410
00:35:43,070 --> 00:35:44,620
I sure did.

411
00:35:45,000 --> 00:35:48,960
Then, please...
teach your indecent slave.

412
00:35:58,610 --> 00:36:03,850
Master, it feels so good... Yes!

413
00:36:06,320 --> 00:36:08,590
It's too good... I'm going to die!

414
00:36:11,090 --> 00:36:15,690
I'm so close... Please... I want to!

415
00:36:44,890 --> 00:36:46,490
Get Kyle for me.

416
00:36:47,530 --> 00:36:49,260
He's probably in that bar.

417
00:36:50,700 --> 00:36:51,760
Y... yes.

418
00:37:06,820 --> 00:37:07,750
Mr. Kyle.

419
00:37:10,620 --> 00:37:12,450
Ah... It's you.

420
00:37:14,060 --> 00:37:16,250
Came to laugh at me?

421
00:37:16,390 --> 00:37:18,120
Mr. Sho is asking for you.

422
00:37:32,410 --> 00:37:34,400
S... Sho!! You!

423
00:37:34,580 --> 00:37:37,050
I have a proposition for you, Kyle.

424
00:37:38,550 --> 00:37:40,680
I will be continuing on my journey.

425
00:37:40,980 --> 00:37:46,940
But two slaves are too much
for me, so I want you to buy...

426
00:37:47,120 --> 00:37:48,720
one of them.

427
00:37:53,430 --> 00:37:55,060
Don't be ridiculous.

428
00:37:55,600 --> 00:37:56,900
I'm serious.

429
00:38:01,900 --> 00:38:05,570
My family has been slave-brokers
for five generations.

430
00:38:08,310 --> 00:38:10,710
Although I did not
take over the business...

431
00:38:13,080 --> 00:38:16,110
