432
00:38:20,660 --> 00:38:22,750
But, my heart says otherwise.

433
00:38:23,490 --> 00:38:26,950
Diana is too customized
for you, Sho.

434
00:38:27,830 --> 00:38:30,990
It's too late to re-train
her as my slave.

435
00:38:31,330 --> 00:38:32,320
Besides...

436
00:38:32,370 --> 00:38:33,560
Besides?

437
00:38:33,700 --> 00:38:36,500
Diana is too proud to be a slave.

438
00:38:37,840 --> 00:38:40,540
