and kill herself.

440
00:38:44,280 --> 00:38:46,440
I don't want that to happen.

441
00:38:47,120 --> 00:38:48,240
Then?

442
00:38:53,090 --> 00:38:54,720
I'll buy Patris.

443
00:38:57,430 --> 00:39:02,020
