446
00:39:11,170 --> 00:39:13,160
One copper coin?!

447
00:39:16,510 --> 00:39:18,100
Is it too much, Kyle?

448
00:39:18,380 --> 00:39:21,210
N... no!! I'll pay you right now.

449
00:39:22,220 --> 00:39:25,240
Before you change your mind. Here!!

450
00:39:28,190 --> 00:39:33,420
The payment has been duly received.
She is now yours.

451
00:39:37,230 --> 00:39:38,290
Patris...

452
00:39:38,700 --> 00:39:41,000
Do you want to be like Diana here?

453
00:39:45,010 --> 00:39:46,910
Want to be a precious woman?

454
00:39:47,480 --> 00:39:50,240
A woman who takes pleasure
in being taken by a man?

455
00:39:51,080 --> 00:39:52,240
Mr. Kyle...

456
00:39:57,150 --> 00:40:00,380
Mr. Kyle... Please take me now!

457
00:40:01,120 --> 00:40:02,150
Patris!

458
00:40:02,190 --> 00:40:03,120
Master!

459
00:40:03,830 --> 00:40:06,190
I've been in love
with you for so long...

460
00:40:06,460 --> 00:40:08,120
I did everything...

461
00:40:08,460 --> 00:40:11,260
like you told me to,
so you'd like me.

462
00:40:12,030 --> 00:40:15,470
I have been waiting for this day.

463
00:40:17,570 --> 00:40:18,970
Mr. Kyle.

464
00:40:21,510 --> 00:40:24,480
I am forever your slave.

465
00:40:27,750 --> 00:40:28,770
Kyle.

466
00:40:29,720 --> 00:40:31,710
A gift for her.

467
00:40:32,820 --> 00:40:34,220
What's this for?

468
00:40:34,920 --> 00:40:37,590
Have her keep it on her.

469
00:40:38,330 --> 00:40:41,420
As long as she remembers how
much she was sold for...

470
00:40:41,460 --> 00:40:43,460
