471
00:40:45,230 --> 00:40:46,960
That's a good idea.

472
00:40:47,070 --> 00:40:51,170
I'll make her a gold necklace
with this coin embedded in it.

473
00:40:53,080 --> 00:40:56,910
If Patris wishes so, I will spend
her entire fortune on the necklace.

474
00:40:58,950 --> 00:41:02,010
Kyle, slaves are not
allowed to keep any assets.

475
00:41:03,590 --> 00:41:05,920
Patris isn't wearing my collar.

476
00:41:05,960 --> 00:41:07,050
Not yet.

477
00:41:08,960 --> 00:41:11,450
You devil!

478
00:41:13,460 --> 00:41:16,330
If she marries Kyle
as a free person...

479
00:41:16,370 --> 00:41:19,100
she can inherit all
of her family's fortune.

480
00:41:20,240 --> 00:41:22,670
So, Kyle is not going
to make her wear a collar...

481
00:41:22,710 --> 00:41:24,800
even if she is treated
as a slave in private.

482
00:41:25,110 --> 00:41:26,370
Right, Kyle?

483
00:41:27,310 --> 00:41:30,400
