487
00:41:41,690 --> 00:41:43,890
Diana, I thank you, too.

488
00:41:45,560 --> 00:41:48,830
Diana, Patris is busy
taking her lessons.

489
00:41:49,470 --> 00:41:51,060
We shouldn't bother her.

490
00:41:51,470 --> 00:41:54,230
You are the one who sold her.

491
00:41:58,110 --> 00:41:59,270
Master?

492
00:42:00,240 --> 00:42:01,070
What?

493
00:42:01,140 --> 00:42:04,810
