tying up women?

494
00:42:05,880 --> 00:42:07,870
Well, it wasn't with me.

495
00:42:08,780 --> 00:42:11,840
Well, it's been 12 years...
there was plenty of time to learn.

496
00:42:14,190 --> 00:42:16,750
No, not for me!!

497
00:42:17,460 --> 00:42:18,620
I guess not.

498
00:42:18,790 --> 00:42:21,190
You were still a virgin
when you met me.

499
00:42:22,130 --> 00:42:23,360
