I need to rest.

502
00:42:32,140 --> 00:42:36,100
You didn't sleep at all last night.
Do you want to rest with me?

503
00:42:36,950 --> 00:42:38,810
You really are going to sleep?

504
00:42:39,250 --> 00:42:41,550
That would be up to you.

505
00:42:41,950 --> 00:42:44,510
That's not fair, Master!

506
00:42:51,660 --> 00:43:03,770
In a pair of yearning eyes,
I fall into a dream...

507
00:43:05,210 --> 00:43:17,090
and again the hard
wind blows in.

508
00:43:22,120 --> 00:43:34,090
Turning back the long
way I have come...

509
00:43:35,570 --> 00:43:47,450
the shadows of flowers
are swaying in the wind.

510
00:43:52,560 --> 00:44:09,060
In the sky, a bird cries out.

511
00:44:12,810 --> 00:44:32,820
Although the pain in my
heart brings me down...

512
00:44:33,200 --> 00:44:38,860
with you...

513
00:44:43,340 --> 00:44:48,970
someday...

514
00:44:50,110 --> 00:44:55,570
someday...

515
00:44:56,920 --> 00:45:14,600
